{"tid":1473540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唯一生路，兩路大軍伐機場","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:23.000Z","uid":190579,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba9c9a22eedf6b38bb9891fd25a48ad52f6d9f8","tid":1473540,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:14:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間：<span style=\"color: red;\">未定</span></span>，一定係818之後<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一路軍：</span></ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所有有車人士慢駛</span>入機場，入到赤蠟角後唔好落車，慢駛出番去，七進七出，收赤蠟角陸路交通皮。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一架車既力量，係抵100個年輕人既肉身！</span></span></strong><br />\n號召所有中產父母，打呢條係最輕鬆最安全最高效既戰線。<br />\n唔好猶豫，冇藉口退縮！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二路軍：</span></ins><br />\n全部青衣站轉機鐵。機場已佈置好水馬，陸路入唔到。錢既問題唔使擔心，到時就會有。入到機場後同鬼佬共同進退，鬼佬留我留，鬼佬撤我撤。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>裝備：</ins></span><br />\n替換既衫<br />\n充分食物同水<br />\n(重要) 有Gib 既拖枕頭同被入去，目標係令鬼佬可以舒舒服服留喺機場，解決佢哋出去搵酒店既需要，原因自己諗 <br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">軍規</span></ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔衝禁區<br />\n唔打鬼佬 記者 first aid<br />\n唔捉鬼</span>"},{"pid":"b1552fec4688a3a4c525a4a3f3c52a68895d21fd","tid":1473540,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91449860fd07f0ff0f9bf259a9ff556cbf3257ff","tid":1473540,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08845ce24dd10aed9f34f06b6497ef00854ad0b1","tid":1473540,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a4c4b8e7394da1908c82f8b36e467aad01fdf5","tid":1473540,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b5f95c995bf425794d97d56b1445378b2fed7a","tid":1473540,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895d51ce768b98b0c4b854b85154b3f1eb34a424","tid":1473540,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"吓, 咩你唔知香港而家有個新牌練習好去處?<br />\n起點喺北大嶼山公路, 一直沿路入機場路, 再經機場南迴旋處同航天城迴旋處轉入赤鱲角路, 到達大白象人工島後繼續直去, 就可以去返連接路返回北大嶼山公路往東涌方向, 繼續練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路線呈環形, 有時速限制110公里既高速公路, 又有兩個迴旋處俾你LOOP住黎練, 練到肚餓可以去機場食飯, 又可以去機場同大白象人工島各個停車場練習泊位掉頭, 全科練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提示: P牌記得唔好行過70呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新牌都最好慢慢行, 唔好急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c66f4bccc7488898f6a7a39c4723358f3a32bcc","tid":1473540,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:40:18.000Z","msg":"順時針方向<br />\nimg]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/C5Vhx2R.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5Vhx2R.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=d9f78104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/C5Vhx2R.png[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n逆時針方向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOOEH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvOOEH2.png&h=1ff8493e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfdbec68a33caff0ec4238c299b5111631ab15d8","tid":1473540,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順時針方向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5Vhx2R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5Vhx2R.png&h=c4